## 2. Module Structure Class Diagram (Artifact 2)

```plantuml
@startuml
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor White
  ArrowColor Black
  BorderColor Black
}
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Courier"

class ConfigTraining {
  + String SSD_ROOT
  + String NPY_DIR
  + String DATASET_DIR
  + int NUM_CLASSES = 100
  + int MAX_SEQUENCE_LENGTH = 20
  + int FRAME_WIDTH = 320
  + int FRAME_HEIGHT = 240
  + int MODEL_COMPLEXITY = 0
  + float MIN_DETECTION_CONFIDENCE = 0.6
  + float MIN_TRACKING_CONFIDENCE = 0.5
}

class PreprocessingCore {
  + float[] normalize_hand_landmarks(float[] hand_row)
  + float[] normalize_frame(float[] frame_hands)
  + float[][] normalize_sequence(float[][] seq_hands)
}

class ExtractHands {
  + List find_videos()
  + float[][] extract_landmarks_from_video(String video_path, Hands detector)
}

class BuildDataset {
  + float[][] pad_or_truncate(float[][] sequence, int max_len)
  + List collect_samples()
  + tuple build_arrays(List samples)
}

class ConvertTfliteSimple {
  + Model load_model()
  + dict _strip_quantization_config(dict obj)
}

class TestWebcamLive {
  + Mat draw_text(Mat frame_bgr, String text, Point position)
  + tuple extract_and_normalize_hands(results)
}

ConfigTraining <.. ExtractHands : references
ConfigTraining <.. BuildDataset : references
PreprocessingCore <.. BuildDataset : uses
PreprocessingCore <.. TestWebcamLive : uses
ConvertTfliteSimple ..> ConfigTraining : references
@endum
```

